OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FPakistan has said it is at "open war"
OL,7,Fwith Afghanistan after launching what
OL,8,Fit described as retaliatory strikes
OL,9,Fagainst its neighbour, as tensions
OL,10,Fcontinue to escalate between the two
OL,11,Fcountries.
OL,13,FPakistan's defence minister said his
OL,14,Fcountry had run out of "patience" with
OL,15,FAfghanistan after both sides launched
OL,16,Fstrikes. Pakistan maintains its
OL,17,Fstrikes were carried out in
OL,18,Fretaliation.
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@eO]vD@XOUvD@aO]
