OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772265857
OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Defence Minister
OL,7,FKhawaja Mohammad Asif said Pakistan
OL,8,Fhad hoped for peace in Afghanistan
OL,9,Fafter the withdrawal of Nato forces
OL,10,Fand expected the Taliban to focus on
OL,11,Fthe welfare of the Afghan people and
OL,12,Fregional stability. Instead, he
OL,13,Falleged, the Taliban had turned
OL,14,FAfghanistan "into a colony of India",
OL,15,Fharboured militants from around the
OL,16,Fworld and begun "exporting terrorism".
OL,18,F"Our patience has now run out. Now it
OL,19,Fis open war between us," he said.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@dO]xD@QOUxD@eO]zD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
