PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772265857
OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FHis remarks came hours after Pakistani
OL,7,Fairstrikes reportedly targeted sites
OL,8,Fin Kabul, as well as Kandahar in the
OL,9,Fsouth and Paktia Province in the
OL,10,Fsoutheast. The escalation comes months
OL,11,Fafter Qatar and Turkey mediated a
OL,12,Fceasefire between the two sides.
OL,14,FPakistan has frequently accused India
OL,15,Fof backing the outlawed Baloch
OL,16,FLiberation Army and the Pakistani
OL,17,FTaliban, allegations New Delhi denies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
