OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FBoth governments have issued
OL,7,Fconflicting casualty figures, each
OL,8,Fclaiming to have inflicted heavy
OL,9,Flosses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
