PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772265857
OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FAfghanistan's Defence Ministry said
OL,7,Fovernight that 55 Pakistani soldiers
OL,8,Fhad been killed, including some whose
OL,9,Fbodies were taken into Afghanistan,
OL,10,Fand that "several others were captured
OL,11,Falive." It said eight Afghan soldiers
OL,12,Fwere killed and 11 injured. The
OL,13,Fministry said it destroyed 19
OL,14,FPakistani army posts and two bases and
OL,15,Fthat the fighting ended around
OL,16,Fmidnight, about four hours after it
OL,17,Fbegan Thursday.
