PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772265857
OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FPakistan's Information Minister
OL,7,FAttaullah Tarar said two Pakistani
OL,8,Fsoldiers were killed and three injured
OL,9,Fand denied that the soldiers had been
OL,10,Fcaptured.
OL,12,FMosharraf Ali Zaidi, a spokesperson
OL,13,Ffor Pakistan's Prime Minister Shehbaz
OL,14,FSharif, claimed in a post on X, that
OL,15,Fat least 133 Afghan fighters were
OL,16,Fkilled and more than 200 injured. He
OL,17,Falso said 27 Afghan posts were
OL,18,Fdestroyed and nine fighters captured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
