PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772265857
OL,3,CPakistan at 'open war' with
OL,4,CAfghanistan after latest strikes
OL,6,FAsif accused the Taliban government of
OL,7,Fdenying Afghans basic human rights,
OL,8,Fincluding women's rights, which he
OL,9,Fsaid are guaranteed under Islam.
